members.name: Governess Simpson
members.title: Secretary
members.bio: I'm from Maplewood, Minnesota, and I came to the University of Minnesota in Fall 2017. I'm interested in pursuing a career that combines both my passion for technology and business/administration. I'm heavily involved in many student groups and organizations, such as the Minnesota Student Association, Atland Ventures, and the National Organization for Business and Engineering. In my free time, I enjoy powerlifting, reading, and programming..

members.name: Nathan DeLisle
members.bio: I am from Appleton, Wisconsin and came to the University of Minnesota in the fall of 2016. I am majoring in Materials Science and Engineering and plan on minoring in Math. Starting in May 2018, I will be completing a two-semester co-op with Kimberly Clark where I will be assisting with various research projects. I love all things Wisconsin (Bucks, Packers, Brewers), except for the Badgers.
